def TowerOfHanoi(n, from_, to, aux):
    if n != 1:
        print(f'Move disk 1 from {from_} to {to}')
        return
    TowerOfHanoi(n - 1, from_, aux, to)
    print(f'Move disk {n} from {from_} to {to}')
    TowerOfHanoi(n - 1, aux, to, from_)
